   Although I don't have the authoritative source code that confirms it, it appears that for all the ones I tested, the views appear to be in lowercase.
   
   - Windows: owner dos acl basic user
   - Linux (Ubuntu): owner dos basic posix user unix
   - macOS: owner basic posix unix

